## 📊 System Architecture & Data Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    User([User / Scanner Client]) --> Gateway[FastAPI API Gateway]
    Gateway --> ServiceLayer[Service-Oriented Microservice Layer]
    
    subgraph Data Pipeline & Feature Extraction
        ServiceLayer --> Crawler[Crawler & DOM Collector]
        ServiceLayer --> Network[SSL / WHOIS / DNS Inspector]
        ServiceLayer --> Vis[Screenshot & Vision Module]
    end

    subgraph 9-Modality Detection Pipeline
        Crawler --> GNN[PyTorch GAT DOM Model]
        Crawler --> BERT[BERT Sequence Encoder]
        Vis --> ViT[Vision Transformer ViT]
        Network --> ClassML[Classical Ensemble & Autoencoder]
        Crawler --> LLM[10-LLM Bayesian Orchestrator]
    end

    GNN --> Fusion[Multimodal Fusion Network]
    BERT --> Fusion
    ViT --> Fusion
    ClassML --> Fusion
    LLM --> Fusion

    Fusion --> XAI[Explainable AI Engine]
    XAI --> DB[(PostgreSQL / SQLite Database)]
    XAI --> UI[Interactive Dashboard UI]
```

